Jadiii, Tolong diisi yah teman -temannnn ‚ò∫Ô∏èüéâüëçüèª Kelompok kami juga akan sangat berterima kasih bila kalian bisa membantu membagikan form survey kami, dan tentu saja sesuai dgn prosedur berikut: 
Utk mahasiswa universitas lain -utk NIM, kalian diharapkan mengisi form ini dgn nama universitas kalian. Utk jurusan bisa diisi seperti yang tertulis

Utk para siswa/siswi SMA - utk NIM, kalian diharapkan mengisi form ini dgn nama sekolah beserta kelas kalian. Utk jurusan kalian bisa isi di 'others' jurusan kalian (cth; IPA, IPS, Animasi, dsb) atau jurusan yang akan kalian pilih ketika berkuliah nanti.

Utk para siswa/siswi SMP dan SD yang dari kelas 4-6 - utk NIM, kalian diharapkan mengisi form ini dengan nama sekolah dan kelas kalian. Utk jurusan, kalian diharapkan mengisi bagian 'others' dgn kelas kalian lagi. Utk adik-adik yg masih duduk di bangku sekolah dasar, kalian diharapkan mengisi form ini dgn kakak ataupun orang tua kalian ü§ìü§óüëç Bagi para siswa/siswi SMA, SMP, dan SD

"Lost in Time" : years pass quickly as Svetluska grown into a healthy little girl. But as Svetluska grew, Chronos become restless. He felt Svetluska grow too fast for him. He realized that even thought she was his own daughter & brought to life by his own breath. She was still human, the fact that had been forgotten by him. So, on her fifth birthday Chronos gave her a choker. It was made by gold and infused by his own power. On it, engraved circle-like shape that attach to one another. A "Timeless-Infinity". Chronos hope that this choker will slow down Svetluska grown, and cheated her age to Grim Reaper. But after 100 years, all of those things changed. By the time of her 105 birthday, The Grim reaper come to Chronos's dimension, demanded for Svetluska soul. Chronos who afraid that her own daughter life, take her to Earth. He take her to the place where he found her's body. After 105 years, the cold mountain had turn into a green and warm place. Below, a new civilization is build. Believing that the place save enough to his own daughter, Chronos left her there to an old couple who lived on the outskirt town. He change their memory into believing that Svetluska was their own granddaughter. Svetluska, who still in appearance of 10 years old had a big knowledge of all the dimension & their each tradition, fit into her new life perfectly. Before Chronos left, he changed the choker spells to make her aging normally without making her into old-&-dust. He told her that for now, she can lived hidden as a normal human until Grim anger subside. "Time halt stop when you smile, while my heart beats like a broken time. For thee are my own kin, i shalt protect thee with all my might", with those words he left a kiss on her temple and dissappear in the thin air...( To Be Continued...) #daisukiclub_join4 #anime #sketch #manga #illust #illustration #oc #draw #doodle #design

caption.text: Lost in Time : Svetluska was create by her father, Chronos due to loneliness of living alone in "timeless" dimension. He make a deal with a Grim Reaper in exchange for a soul of "Hollow" or a soul without any trace of kindness nor evil. Chronos then began his journey from one time to another, seeking an empty vessels for a soul he acquired. After "jump" from time to time, he found a vessel, a body of a dead baby girl. The body was found in the blizzard night on a mountain of snow, she was left there to died. Chronos then place a soul he kept into the baby, and breathe to her face. The baby come to life, and start crying, seeking for heat. Chronos wrap the baby with his robe and come back to his dimension, while rocking the baby in his arm. Her hair and eyes were in soft caramel, her skin was soft and milky white with a pinkish color. The baby stop crying and grab a handful of Chronos's robe while leaning her body to Chronos chest with a serene look and smile. Looking to her smile, A small smile crept on his face as he look upon his new daughter. His chest feels warm and full of joy because the baby in his arm. Then in happiness he said:"When first star come alight, born there first soul to reside. Bring happiness upon my frozen heart, for thou shalt be my light". And after that, he named her Svetluska Allegra.... (To be continued) #daisukiclub_join4 #anime #manga #sketch
